    <article>
        <p>The following articles were written between mid-2012 and early 2013, during which time I had challenged myself to publish a new article, every day of the week, on my blog. I managed to maintain this pace for several months, before my move from Canada to London, England began to occupy all my available energies. I hope to one day pick up such a regular writing schedule again!</p>
        <p>Tapping the article titles will open them in a new window; they are presented true-to-form, in their original layout, with their contents unedited &mdash; as such, you may find some broken links along the way, but I think that just adds to the charm.</p>
        <p>You can return to this page by closing the new window, or tapping the &ldquo;home&rdquo; icon on the article pages.</p>
        <p><em>(By the way, my more recent writing is and will continue to be published <a href="http://medium.com/@cole_peters">here</a>.)</em></p>
    </article>
